zhnGPONLink.name: zhnGPONLink

revisions.description: Added the following objects: txPower txBiasCurrent gponTemperature gponVcc

zhnGPONLink.contactinfo: Zhone Technologies, Inc. Florida Design Center 8545 126th Avenue North Largo, FL 33773 Toll-Free: +1 877-ZHONE20 (+1 877-946-6320) Tel: +1-510-777-7000 Fax: +1-510-777-7001 E-mail: support@zhone.com
zhnGPONLink.description: This file defines the private Enterprise MIB extensions that define GPON interface related objects supported by the Zhone VoIP CPEs.

GPONLinkStatusValues.name: GPONLinkStatusValues
GPONLinkStatusValues.description: GPON interface status. An enumeration of: Up Down Initializing Unavailable

GPONEnabledDisabledStatusValues.name: GPONEnabledDisabledStatusValues
GPONEnabledDisabledStatusValues.description: GPON RF Video status. An enumeration of: Disabled Enabled

GPONStateValues.name: GPONStateValues
GPONStateValues.description: GPON ONU state. An enumeration of: INIT STANDBY SERIAL NUMBER RANGING OPERATIONAL POPUP EMERGENCY STOP DEACTIVATED

GPONOnOffAlarmValues.name: GPONOnOffAlarmValues
GPONOnOffAlarmValues.description: GPON Alarm status. An enumeration of: On Off

gponInterfaceNumberOfEntries.name: gponInterfaceNumberOfEntries
gponInterfaceNumberOfEntries.description: Number of instances of GPON interfaces for this ONU.

gponLinkStatusTable.name: gponLinkStatusTable
gponLinkStatusTable.description: Table of GPON link status information.

gponLinkStatusEntry.name: gponLinkStatusEntry
gponLinkStatusEntry.description: Table of GPON link status information.

gponOperStatus.name: gponOperStatus
gponOperStatus.description: Indicates the status of this GPON interface. Enumeration of: Up Down Initializing Unavailable

gponLinkUpTransitions.name: gponLinkUpTransitions
gponLinkUpTransitions.description: Number of times the GPON link has transitioned from down to up.

rfVideo.name: rfVideo
rfVideo.description: Indicates if the RF Video over the GPON interface is enabled or disabled. Enumeration of: Disabled Enabled

gponState.name: gponState
gponState.description: Optical network unit state. Enumeration of: INIT STANDBY SERIAL NUMBER RANGING OPERATIONAL POPUP EMERGENCY STOP DEACTIVATED

rxLevel.name: rxLevel
rxLevel.description: GPON interface receive level, in dBm.

txPower.name: txPower
txPower.description: GPON interface transmit power, in dBm.

txBiasCurrent.name: txBiasCurrent
txBiasCurrent.description: GPON interface transmit bias current, in mA.

gponTemperature.name: gponTemperature
gponTemperature.description: GPON interface diplexer/triplexer temperature, in Celsius.

gponAlarmStatusTable.name: gponAlarmStatusTable
gponAlarmStatusTable.description: Table of GPON alarm status information.

gponAlarmStatusEntry.name: gponAlarmStatusEntry
gponAlarmStatusEntry.description: Table of GPON alarm status information.

gponAlarmAutoPowerControlFail.name: gponAlarmAutoPowerControlFail
gponAlarmAutoPowerControlFail.description: If the value of this object is ON, the automatic power-control has failed.

gponAlarmLOS.name: gponAlarmLOS
gponAlarmLOS.description: If the value of this object is ON, no input signal has been detected. Make sure fiber is plugged in.

gponAlarmLOL.name: gponAlarmLOL
gponAlarmLOL.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has detected a Loss of Link condition.

gponAlarmLOF.name: gponAlarmLOF
gponAlarmLOF.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has detected a Loss Of Frame condition.

gponAlarmLCDG.name: gponAlarmLCDG
gponAlarmLCDG.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has detected a Loss of GEM Channel Delineation condition.

gponAlarmFailedSignal.name: gponAlarmFailedSignal
gponAlarmFailedSignal.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has detected a bit error rate greater than 10E-5.

gponAlarmDegradedSignal.name: gponAlarmDegradedSignal
gponAlarmDegradedSignal.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has detected a bit error rate greater than 10E-6.

gponAlarmStartupFail.name: gponAlarmStartupFail
gponAlarmStartupFail.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has detected an error during startup.

gponAlarmMsgErrorMsg.name: gponAlarmMsgErrorMsg
gponAlarmMsgErrorMsg.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has received an unknown PLOAM message.

gponAlarmDeactivateOnuId.name: gponAlarmDeactivateOnuId
gponAlarmDeactivateOnuId.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has received a de-activate request and has successfully de-activated the link.

gponAlarmDisabledOnu.name: gponAlarmDisabledOnu
gponAlarmDisabledOnu.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has been disabled by the OLT or the ONU Serial Number is not configured on the OLT.

gponAlarmPEE.name: gponAlarmPEE
gponAlarmPEE.description: If the value of this object is ON, the GPON link has detected a physical equipment error which may indicate a possible hardware problem.

gponDataGemStatsTable.name: gponDataGemStatsTable

gponDataGemStatsEntry.name: gponDataGemStatsEntry
gponDataGemStatsEntry.description: Table of GPON Encapsulation Method (GEM) VoIP and Internet traffic statistics for the Data GEM port.

dataGemPortTxDroppedFrames.name: dataGemPortTxDroppedFrames

dataGemPortAcceptedMulticastFrames.name: dataGemPortAcceptedMulticastFrames

dataGemPortDroppedMulticastFrames.name: dataGemPortDroppedMulticastFrames
dataGemPortDroppedMulticastFrames.description: Number of multicast frames dropped by the Multicast Filtering Function.

videoGemPortRxFrames.description: Number of ethernet frames received on the video GEM port.

videoGemPortRxDroppedFrames.name: videoGemPortRxDroppedFrames

gponGtcStatsTable.name: gponGtcStatsTable
gponGtcStatsTable.description: Table of GPON Transmission Convergence (GTC) statistics for the Data GEM port.

gponGtcStatsEntry.name: gponGtcStatsEntry
gponGtcStatsEntry.description: Table of GPON Transmission Convergence (GTC) statistics for the Data GEM port.

gtcTotalRxDsFecCodewords.name: gtcTotalRxDsFecCodewords
gtcTotalRxDsFecCodewords.description: Total Received Downstream Forward Error Coding Codewords.

gtcFecCorrectionSeconds.name: gtcFecCorrectionSeconds
gtcFecCorrectionSeconds.description: Number of seconds during which there was a FEC correction anomaly.

gtcCorrectedHecErrorsGemFrames.name: gtcCorrectedHecErrorsGemFrames
gtcCorrectedHecErrorsGemFrames.description: Number of GEM frames with corrected HEC errors.

gtcUncorrectableHecErrorsGemFrames.name: gtcUncorrectableHecErrorsGemFrames
gtcUncorrectableHecErrorsGemFrames.description: Number of GEM frames with uncorrectable HEC errors.

gponPloamStatsEntry.description: Table of GPON Physical Layer Operation, Administration and Management (PLOAM) statistics for the Data GEM port.

msgsCrcError.name: msgsCrcError
msgsCrcError.description: Messages received in error and discarded.

msgsRxTotal.name: msgsRxTotal
msgsRxTotal.description: Total Number of CRC correct downstream PLOAM messages received.

msgsRxUnicast.name: msgsRxUnicast
msgsRxUnicast.description: Number of CRC correct downstream PLOAM messages with ONU ID matching this ONU's ID.

msgsRxBroadcast.name: msgsRxBroadcast
msgsRxBroadcast.description: Number of CRC correct broadcast downstream PLOAM messages.

msgsRxDiscarded.name: msgsRxDiscarded
msgsRxDiscarded.description: Number of downstream PLOAM messages discarded, because the message is unknown and not registered, or because the message is not valid in the current state.

msgsRxNonStandard.name: msgsRxNonStandard
msgsRxNonStandard.description: Number of non-standard downstream PLOAM messages received from the OLT.

msgsTxTotal.name: msgsTxTotal
msgsTxTotal.description: Total number of PLOAM messages transmitted upstream to the OLT.

msgsTxNonStandard.name: msgsTxNonStandard
msgsTxNonStandard.description: Number of non-standard PLOAM messages transmitted upstream to the OLT.
